description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Transforming emotions | Guided Meditation By Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar' from the channel Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: "Transforming Emotions" guided meditation by Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar, gives us the much-needed relief from negative emotions. It gives you a sense of deep relaxation and enables you to effortlessly experience a positive state of mind. Additionally, this meditation will improve your concentration.

About #Gurudev:
World-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Through his life and work, Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar has inspired millions around the world with a vision of a stress-free and violence-free world. Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives across the world.
